#: ../../../contributing/design.md:1
msgid "Design Notes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../contributing/design.md:3
msgid "Reason for existence"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../contributing/design.md:5
msgid ""
"Furo exists because, at the time of writing, no existing Sphinx "
"documentation theme quite fit what I wanted. The rough structural elements I "
"wanted were:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../contributing/design.md:7
msgid "Three-column layout, for proper in-page navigation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../contributing/design.md:8
msgid "Clear navigational sidebar."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../contributing/design.md:9
msgid "Good search."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../contributing/design.md:10
msgid "Good typography."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../contributing/design.md:11
msgid "Good looking design."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../contributing/design.md:13
msgid ""
"Every existing theme either didn't check all of the boxes above, or tried to "
"do too many things at the same time. There were a few that came close, but "
"nothing really felt quite polished to me."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../contributing/design.md:15
msgid "\"Guiding\" ideas"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../contributing/design.md:17
msgid ""
"Furo's design follows a few of the ideas I've had discovered over the course "
"of browsing the existing documentation themes across ecosystems and static "
"site generators."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../contributing/design.md:19
msgid "Focus _must_ be on the content."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../contributing/design.md:20
msgid "More stuff is not more good."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../contributing/design.md:21
msgid "Graceful degradation is important, so are niceties."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../contributing/design.md:22
msgid "Simple and good enough, is more than sufficient."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../contributing/design.md:23
msgid "This is for the 80% -- don't need to cover all possible usecases."
msgstr ""
